      • numberOfYears

        public int numberOfYears()

        This method returns the number of years a customer is active on current mobile service by calculating number of years between account opening date and current system date.


        If a customer opens their account on 02/29/2016, this method will return 3, i.e number of years the customer is active on this connection.
        Hint: You can use LocalDate and ChronoUnit class.
        Returns:
        number of years of type int
